column26: My wife is the most incredible person in the world. There are innumerable ways she helps me. If I had to pick one, she loves and validates me and makes me feel valued and loved.
column27: If I had to pick a second, she believes in me and encourages me to pursue my dreams more than I thought I should and it has always culminated in success thanks to her immaculate judgement.

column11: Listen to me complain about work and actually listened
column12: Ordered dinner after a long shift so it would be there when I got home
column13: Covered me up when I fell asleep on the couch
column14: Took the dog out when he got up before I did
column15: Picked up wine after a long week
column16: Asked me how I was doing
column17: Acknowledged how hard I have been working and encouraged me to keep going
column19: Picked me up from work when it was raining
column20: Told me he loves me and never lets me forget
